snippet.title: Tray Racers! | Gameplay Trailer | Future Games Show June 2022
snippet.description:
World premiere time! Enjoy this brand new gameplay trailer from Tray Racers!.
First debuted at the Future Games Show in June 2022.
Tray Racers! is the next game from the team that brought you the delightful co-op puzzler Phogs.
Tray Racers! is coming to PC and Nintendo Switch in 2023
